Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然中了流彈…真不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能死在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.09,0:00:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的夢想該怎麼辦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.48,0:00:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫相良…良晴是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有一國一城美女如雲的夢想  你來替我去實現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.87,0:00:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊  良晴  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊  我還不知道大叔你的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是…木下藤吉郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤吉郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是豐臣秀吉嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  別死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死了歷史就要變得亂七八糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.49,0:00:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要為信長效力  統一天下…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信長？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:01:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田家的主公…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.27,0:01:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是織田…信奈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔——！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是搞什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.15,0:01:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  一定是在做夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是「信長公的野望」的大粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在玩遊戲的時候不小心睡著了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女…女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下的人頭  在下收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼可以這樣對待美少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:01:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  你也是織田的兵嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤手空拳的想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  還真沒多想就上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點收拾他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都行  必須做點什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵…敵人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「信長公的野望」  下載特典
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合戰之聲！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小盒子裡有大軍團嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這傢伙  是妖術師嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕了吧  那麼就快點…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊…忘記充電了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上！把他們兩個都砍了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就GAME OVER了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  如果是我代替她死的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  是鬼柴田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  還差一步就能幹掉織田的總大將了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田的總大將…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣一口氣趕走今川吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備騎到什麼時候啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個小小的足輕居然敢推倒織田家的主公
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主公…不是織田信長嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「信長」是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田的主公可是本小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田信奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:07.03,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誓いの刃  振るう刹那  感触
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:11.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そして  また傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:15.83,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}唇を  噛み締めながら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:21.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何が  正しいのかと問おう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:26.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなた  守る  でもその前に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:30.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}果たすべきことがあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:38.19,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}特別  何かになりたいんじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:41.53,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}私  嘘つきたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:46.66,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}命をかけて  荒野を駆ける戦いの日々の中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:51.91,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}振り向くと  そこにいて  震え止めてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:56.83,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}哀しみの火が閉じれば  昇り火が昇る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:59.68,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}運命  蹴っ飛ばし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.01,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思うまま進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:07.62,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}世界をリンクして
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:07.03,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誓言之刃  觸摸  亢奮的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:11.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}隨之遍體鱗傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:15.83,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊咬雙唇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:21.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}詢問正義之道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:26.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我會保護你  但在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:30.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}有必須要完成的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:38.19,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}並不是想成為特別的「那個」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:41.53,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我不想騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:46.66,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}賭上性命  馳騁在曠野上戰鬥中的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:51.91,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}驀然回首  因為有你  我的心才不再顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:56.83,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悲傷之炎終將熄滅  希望將浴火重生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:59.68,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}擺脫命運束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.01,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝著夢想前進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:07.62,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}連結世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
